these are the differences i noticed ⬇️

1. the shade “chai” looks lighter and has more of pinks. I compared it with the previous purchase and thought the old one looks more brown and dark. It used to be my perfect everyday shade 🫠

2. Like shown in the video, the formula crumbles on my lips after the lipstick dries. What surprises me even more is that, the brand has mentioned there has been no change in the formula, yet I feel something has definitely changed. 

3. ( this is weird ) I swatched the lipstick on my hanss yesterday for the reel and totally forgot about it. This morning i noticed it left a pink stain , Lol 🤣 

All these make me feel its definitely not the lipstick I used to like before. I dont know if this is the case with all their revamped lipsticks or maybe did i just get a defected piece?

how to use ? 

take a few drops of the oil, warm it up with your fingers and massage it on your dry skin until all the makeup gets dissolved, Now spray some water and massage again in circular motions ( it will emulsify ). Finally rinse everything with a luke warm water and follow it up with your regular face wash 

*loosen sebaceous filaments not whiteheads & blackheads ( incorrectly mentioned in the reel ) 

Currently on my second bottle of this cleansing oil from @consciouschemistindia . Effortlessly melts away my makeup and leaves skin fresh without drying. Totally recommend it if you are looking for something affordable and does the job well.
